OL,3,CNew scheme to help islanders avoid
OL,4,Cfastest-growing disease in Jersey
OL,6,F'Love your heart' aims to get
OL,7,Fislanders to focus on being physically
OL,8,Factive, eating healthily, and not
OL,9,Fsmoking.
OL,11,F'Stay Sharp' is a reminder to
OL,12,Fregularly challenge the brain which
OL,13,Fcan help protect it through ageing. It
OL,14,Fpromotes learning a language or
OL,15,Fregularly completing brain training
OL,16,Fexercises.
