OL,3,CNew scheme to help islanders avoid
OL,4,Cfastest-growing disease in Jersey
OL,6,F'Keep Connected' focuses on the
OL,7,Fbeneficial effect of participating in
OL,8,Fgroup activities and volunteering.
OL,9,FDementia Jersey gives examples such as
OL,10,Fhaving a coffee with friends, and says
OL,11,Fany social contact is good for our
OL,12,Fbrains.
OL,14,FClaudine Snape, Chief Executive
OL,15,FOfficer of Dementia Jersey, says:
OL,16,F"This is the biggest campaign we've
OL,17,Fever run, but it's such an important
OL,18,Fmessage that it's possible to reduce
OL,19,Fyour risk of dementia that we need to
OL,20,Fthink big.
