OL,3,CNew scheme to help islanders avoid
OL,4,Cfastest-growing disease in Jersey
OL,6,F"That's one of the reasons we're so
OL,7,Fpleased to be partnering with Public
OL,8,FHealth on this campaign."
OL,10,FProfessor Peter Bradley, Director of
OL,11,FPublic Health, says: "Prevention is
OL,12,Fone of the priorities that underpins
OL,13,Fmuch of our work and I'm delighted to
OL,14,Fsee Dementia Jersey lead this campaign
OL,15,Fwhich has prevention at its core.
OL,17,F"The campaign's focus is on
OL,18,Fencouraging islanders to make simple
OL,19,Fchanges now, to dramatically reduce
OL,20,Ftheir risk of Dementia in the future.
